{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act32side", "eventName": "水晶箭行動", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "CR-2", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "不對稱庭園", "storyInfo": "幫助了特克諾的IANA和DOC造訪街頭藝術社區，卻被受整個社區尊敬的老消防員迪亞茲誤會。他們首次體驗社區文化的旅程不得不在躲避追捕的過程中進行。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有什麼我能幫忙的嗎？", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，剩下的就交給我的朋友，她馬上就來。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一接到你的消息我馬上就過來了，你這傢伙是怎麼了？讓我看看！", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.3}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "shake", "random": "true", "power": 5.0, "times": 10.0, "duration": 0.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，欸，你別弄我頭啦，這麼多人你注意點，別掀我裙子。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你這不蠻好的……活蹦亂跳的。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "多虧了這兩位，我發病的時候他們剛好在旁邊，幫了我一把。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，我是醫生，都是該做的。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……這年頭像你一樣的醫生不多了，大多數一聽到我們的情況，跑都來不及。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這位小姐有人照顧，那我們就不久留了……", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，別走啊。這是小店的名片，你們有空務必光顧，按摩推拿一應俱全，你們來都是八折優惠。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，小姐，我不是很需要。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們別客氣，那傢伙手藝不錯，大家有什麼感冒頭痛的都去找她。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#12$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，身為醫生，我對自己的身體狀況大致有瞭解，很健康，不需要額外關注。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#12$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，試過再說。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小姐，我們還是保持距離比較好。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女人聽到IANA的話，退後幾步，從包裡掏出一副手套，戴好後捏了捏手指，發出清脆的咔噠聲。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，離你遠點也能按。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個距離你能碰到我？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，咳咳，我聽說過這種隔空進行的氣功療法，很多資料證實這不過是偽科……呃……", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#9$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只見她的手指在空中輕輕捏過幾下，二人奇異地感受到一股溫熱的力量在按壓自己的肩頸，瞬間，輕鬆與舒爽將他們溫柔地包裹。"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……我感覺壓力和焦慮……一掃而空……", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#6$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是錯覺嗎……我現在舒服得頭皮發麻……啊……", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……誰還管什麼科學……", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#13$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g9_gangsters", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼……你說藥被搶走了？！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可不是開玩笑的，埃內斯托先生，我們的社區裡有很多感染者，他們都需要藥物來控制病情。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "很抱歉，是我和阿萊塔小姐沒能完成運輸任務，造成的損失我們會盡快想辦法彌補。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會想賠錢了事吧？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果找不到，我會想辦法按時賠償你等量的藥品。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，埃內斯托先生……是我太著急了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#3$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些搶藥的人，你們有看到他們的樣子嗎？社區裡人多，說不定能幫忙。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這也是我們覺得蹊蹺的地方，那些人埋伏在半途中突然衝出，似乎是早有準備。羅德島在這裡一向是小心處事，從不與人交惡……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我實在想不出有什麼人會這樣針對我們。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "或許他們就是盯上了你們的藥，抑制劑在黑市的價格可不低。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#8$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在搶奪過程中他們採用的戰術非常專業，動作迅速，乾淨利落……", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那些藥品真的值得讓一群人如此大動干戈嗎？對了，我依稀記得在躲避時還聽到了銃械的聲音。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "銃械……又是專業的傢伙……呵，雷內爾真瞧得起我們啊。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "迪亞茲先生，你覺得這次行動是有人針對社區嗎？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我們與雷內爾也是積怨很久了，只是沒想到……他最終會使用如此下流的手段。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "樓下發生什麼了，怎麼這麼吵？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#4"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……好像是有人在外面病情發作，被好心人送回來了。喲，這裡三層外三層的，圍的全都是來感謝的人。", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對我們好的人，當然是要報答的。讓我看看來的是哪裡的客……", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這幾個怎麼這麼臉熟，感覺在哪裡看過？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#10$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從桌上拿起昨天的報紙，男人草草翻過幾頁找到八卦版，看見標題上赫然寫著：《沒人能忍受他的惡劣性格——雷內爾再次更換保鏢》。"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "旁邊的副標題則是《記者獨家暗訪：四名保鏢兩兩輪換，究竟何方神聖》。"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "stopsound", "attributes": {"channel": "1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘶……這幾張照片裡的人和樓底下出現的人，是不是有些相似得過分了？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呵，這下我們可真得好好報答報答了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "48_g8_slums", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像自己是完全嶄新的一個人了……這種感覺很難形容。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#4$1"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……謝謝你，這種按摩方式太神奇了。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可是我從謝拉格學的傳統按摩術。當年我在暴風雪中登上聖山，當地的聖女看我誠心才決定將這秘術傳授給我。", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拉倒吧，你從敘拉古來這裡都有七八年了，哪裡來的時間去雪境，你們可別信啊，都是虛假廣告。", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#9$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿，你怎麼污人清白呢……", "name": "社區居民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_697_1#1$1"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳，謝謝您的按摩，時候不早了，我們確實也該離開——", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#10$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢著，二位，雷內爾身邊人手眾多，缺了你們兩個辦事應該也不會怎樣。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不如多留一下子，讓我們好好招待。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#13$1"}, {"id": 162, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "老爹，你這氣沖沖的是怎麼了？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#1$1"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還好意思說，你怎麼跟這群搶藥的傢伙混在一起，還把他們帶到社區來了？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……藥？", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#5$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，抑制礦石病的藥！被他們搶走了！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#7$1"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搶走？？那也不可能是他們啊！他們甚至連礦石病是什麼都不知道！", "name": "特克諾"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1212_1#4$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先生，所謂搶藥的事情，我們真的沒頭緒，這中間是不是有誤會？", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#13$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "誤會？雇傭兵打扮，用銃，不是黑鋼的人，這地界除了你們還有誰？", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們只是把這女孩送回到這裡來，僅此而已。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是真有誤會，那你們可得好好向我澄清下。來人，給我抓住他們！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩人看見迪亞茲背後的副手舉起手中的木杖。"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管完全無法想像杖尖的光芒究竟會如何造成殺傷，他們還是本能地感受到了危險的逼近。"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跑，卡提布，跑！！", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#3$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1", "focus": "all"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_magic_m", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 0.3}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 1.0, "g": 1.0, "b": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-50,0", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小心！", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#4$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來啊，拿銃的混蛋！我看你們哪個敢進社區一步！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你跑得也太快了，我追都追不上，那兩個人現在在哪？", "name": "龍舌蘭"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "躲起來了。", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們在那裡傻站著幹什麼？還不趕快去把那兩個人找出來！", "name": "迪亞茲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1214_1#5$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "走，趕緊走！", "name": "迪亞茲的副手"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_ltalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼、呼、呼……那是什麼？魔法？", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "似乎是叫源石技藝的東西，就當是魔法吧。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#8$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我們得先想個辦法離開。幾個出口處都有人把守。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#8$1"}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……掩護我，我來操作雙子分身。", "name": "IANA"}, "figure_art": "avg_4124_iana_1#6$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "已就位。", "name": "DOC"}, "figure_art": "avg_4125_rdoc_1#8$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_button", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_scan", "channel": "1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energybody", "channel": "2"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.1, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.2, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4124_iana_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "posfrom": "200,-50", "posto": 